1. *Zovemo* ga da li je tu. (We are calling him to see if he is here.)
2. Oni *zovemo* svi zajedno. (We are all calling them together.)
3. Trebalo bi da *zovemo* policiju. (We should call the police.)
4. Oni su nam *zovemo* da dođu. (They are calling us to come.)
5. Oni su nam već *zovemo*. (They have already called us.)
6. Čuo sam da su *zovemo* da dođu na sastanak. (I heard they were calling to come to the meeting.)